{
  "id": "69e2bf235995b3ebceef87a4",
  "title": "User CSS の記法に使える文字の一覧",
  "created": 1776467761,
  "updated": 1776470600,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69e2bf235995b3ebceef87a4",
      "text": "User CSS の記法に使える文字の一覧",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467761,
      "updated": 1776467816
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2bf340000000000103bf3",
      "text": "User CSS の記法はリンクの先頭に記号をつけることで表現される。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467764,
      "updated": 1776467813
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2bf4b0000000000103bf5",
      "text": "\t`[* 太字]` [* 太字]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467787,
      "updated": 1776467829
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2bf770000000000103bf6",
      "text": "\t`[- 打ち消し]` [- 打ち消し]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467831,
      "updated": 1776467851
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2bf870000000000103bf7",
      "text": "\tcss を作成する際には `.deco-*` のように deco クラスに対して CSS を適用することで独自の記法を実現する。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467847,
      "updated": 1776468031
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c0010000000000103bf8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467970,
      "updated": 1776467970
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c0020000000000103bf9",
      "text": "deco クラスとして認識される文字の一覧を並べておくと、記法に使える文字の一覧になる。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467970,
      "updated": 1776468013
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2bf340000000000103bf4",
      "text": " .deco",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776467765,
      "updated": 1776469865
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c76a0000000000103c74",
      "text": " \t全ての deco",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469866,
      "updated": 1776469875
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103bfb",
      "text": " .deco-_",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469865,
      "updated": 1776469865
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103bfc",
      "text": " .deco--",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103bfd",
      "text": " .deco-\\,",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103bfe",
      "text": " .deco-\\!",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103bff",
      "text": " .deco-\\.",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c00",
      "text": " .deco-\\'",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c01",
      "text": " .deco-\\\"",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c02",
      "text": " .deco-\\(",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c03",
      "text": " .deco-\\)",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c04",
      "text": " .deco-\\{",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c05",
      "text": " .deco-\\}",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776469192,
      "updated": 1776469196
    },
    {
      "id": "69e2c4c80000000000103c06",
      "text": " .deco-\\*",
